OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FWatch Max Walsh's report
OL,9,FA care leaver from Bristol has
OL,10,Fdescribed feeling "like a ghost" after
OL,11,Fshe was moved between more than 40
OL,12,Fdifferent placements, often miles away
OL,13,Ffrom home.
OL,15,FMia Newman, 19, says the care system
OL,16,Fis "a scary" and "dark place".
OL,18,FIn Bristol last year, for the first
OL,19,Ftime, more than half of children in
OL,20,Fcare were placed outside of the city.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@ROUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
