PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FThe council says they are working to
OL,8,Ftackle the problem by opening more
OL,9,Fchildren's homes in the city and
OL,10,Fbringing children back to their homes
OL,11,Fwhere it is safe to do so.
OL,13,FMia was just 8 years old when she was
OL,14,Ffirst placed into care. She would go
OL,15,Fand live in cities including
OL,16,FWorcester, Gloucester and, at one
OL,17,Fstage, Glasgow. There were a number of
OL,18,Fdifferent local authorities
OL,19,Fresponsible for her care.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
