PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FMia said: "The best way to describe it
OL,8,Fis you just feel like a ghost. You
OL,9,Fdon't feel real. For a child as well,
OL,10,Fnot understanding why you're here, why
OL,11,Fyou're not with your family. You
OL,12,Frestart your life every three months.
OL,13,FIt really makes you feel like you're
OL,14,Fnothing."
OL,16,FMia says she is now happy after
OL,17,Fleaving the care system. She lives at
OL,18,Fher new home with her baby daughter.
OL,19,FBut she now wants to ensure that her
OL,20,Fchild has a better start in life after
OL,21,Fthe disruption she endured.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
