PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FMia said: "It's insane. Especially for
OL,8,Fa child that's made friends, I made
OL,9,Fbonds. To be moved away to a
OL,10,Fcompletely different city, away from
OL,11,Feverything I know. It takes away your
OL,12,Fidentity and who you are as a person."
OL,14,F"I dropped out of school in Year 8 and
OL,15,FI haven't been to school since. When I
OL,16,Fmoved from Bristol Met, that was it."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@fO]vD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
