PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FBut this is an issue across England,
OL,8,Fwhere increasingly children are being
OL,9,Fplaced housed outside their local
OL,10,Fauthority area and more than 20 miles
OL,11,Faway from home.
OL,13,FThe charity Become, which supports
OL,14,Fchildren in care, has started a
OL,15,Fcampaign calling on the government to
OL,16,Fto stop children being placed miles
OL,17,Ffrom their home area when it is not in
OL,18,Ftheir best interests.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FClare Bracey, Director of Policy and
OL,8,FCommunications at Become, says the
OL,9,Fmoves can have a devastating effect.
OL,11,FShe said: "Across the country right
OL,12,Fnow there are 18,000 children in care,
OL,13,F1 in 5 living far away from their
OL,14,Flocal area. Their lives are being
OL,15,Fturned upside down. They are very
OL,16,Fisolated and are moved far away from
OL,17,Ftheir support networks. For some it
OL,18,Fputs them more at risk where people
OL,19,Fare not looking out for them."
OL,26,@sD@KOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
