PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FIris Dukes, 19, from Bristol was first
OL,8,Fplaced into care at fourteen after a
OL,9,Ffamily breakdown. She was very close
OL,10,Fto her nan who lives in Hillfields but
OL,11,Fwas moved to Bath, then Keynsham, and
OL,12,Fthen Weston-super-Mare.
OL,14,FIris said: "It's the fact that you
OL,15,Fknow you're going to move so there is
OL,16,Fno point in getting comfortable and
OL,17,Fthere is no point in getting to know
OL,18,Fyour carers and that's the hard part.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,F"I need my family and I need my
OL,8,Fsupport. And you ripping me from them
OL,9,Fis only going to make me lash out
OL,10,Fmore."
OL,12,FShe knows the moves impacted her
OL,13,Ffriendships, family and education,
OL,14,Fsomething she is now addressing with
OL,15,Fthe help of the charity 1625
OL,16,FIndependent People.
OL,26,@rD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FBut she says, at the time, it was
OL,8,Fright for her. Despite in some
OL,9,Finstances, being given just hours to
OL,10,Fpack up and move from one place to
OL,11,Fanother.
OL,13,FIris added: "It sounds weird to say
OL,14,Fthat but I am grateful for moving, I'm
OL,15,Fgrateful for being moved out but it
OL,16,Fwasn't easy for me or my nan."
OL,18,FBristol City Council says it is
OL,19,Fworking to keep more families together
OL,20,Fand intervene earlier.
OL,26,@uD@MOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
