PN,43510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776435067
OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FCllr Christine Townsend, from Bristol
OL,8,FCity Council, said: "Of course it
OL,9,Fworries us. We don't want to be moving
OL,10,Fchildren around. They're moved for
OL,11,Ftheir own safety or because the
OL,12,Fplacement is broken down.
OL,14,F"It's a measure of the complexity of
OL,15,Ftheir needs but also of how the system
OL,16,Fhas been gutted - we've had covid as
OL,17,Fwell s ten years of austerity."
OL,19,FThe government says the number of
OL,20,Flooked after children has risen
OL,21,Fsharply by 20% over the last decade.
OL,26,@pD@UOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
