OL,3,C'I felt like a ghost': Rise in
OL,4,Cchildren in care being placed miles
OL,5,Cfrom home
OL,7,FThey are investing #2 billion over
OL,8,Fthree years to improve outcomes and
OL,9,Ffocus on stability in placements and
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FSome of this money will be spent on
OL,13,Fhelping to create 10,000 extra foster
OL,14,Fhomes by 2029 and build and renovate
OL,15,Fmore children's homes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
